    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "On the e-commerce example, I used CurrentFilters to do it : \n\n``` js\n<CurrentFilters\n        theme={{\n          root: 'CurrentFilters',\n          filters: {\n            display: 'none',\n          },\n          clearAll: 'CurrentFilters__clearAll btn',\n        }}\n        translations={{\n          clearAll: 'Clear all filters',\n        }}\n      />\n```\n",
